body.content:
Hi,

 

Sandeep has asked to have a weekly strategy meeting around Subscription after discussing what’s next in our UAC Growth meeting this morning.

So I’m transforming the UAC meeting into this Strategy meeting, adding a few other key stakeholders, and moving to 1 hour at 11:00.

 

Some immediate topics for discussion that arose:

  • Concerns that we don’t have a product market fit between our “Maude’s” and the product offering we put into the market
  • Review strategy and product roadmap as relates to the above concerns
  • Review the underlying assumptions of our revenue projection model
  • Review Marketing/Ad strategy, our spend/month, and is this missing from our projection model

 

Thanks,

Louis

events.subject: Guitar Workshop w/ James Santiago
events.bodyPreview: Come hang with guitar guru James Santiago for deep guitar geekery! Keep your eyes peeled for special guests…so far we’ve had Vernon Reid, Steve Vai, Dweezil Zappa, Richard Fortus, Charlie Hunter, Matt Scannon, Oz Noy, John Shanks, Josh Smith, Colin Hay, A

body.content:
Come hang with guitar guru James Santiago for deep guitar geekery! Keep your eyes peeled for special guests…so far we’ve had Vernon Reid, Steve Vai, Dweezil Zappa, Richard Fortus, Charlie Hunter, Matt Scannon, Oz Noy, John Shanks, Josh Smith, Colin Hay, Art Thompson from Guitar Player, executives from Fender, and more. Who else will stop by?

 

Part guitar lesson, tone workshop, and music history course, we’ll cover it all.

 

  • Playing techniques from country and jazz to rock and blues
  • Advanced music theory for guitar made easy
  • Tips for improving your improvisational skills
  • How to get inspired by non-guitar influences
  • How to dial in everything from vintage amps and pedals to desktop plugins
  • General music appreciation
  • How to sound like you

 

Join the Zoom Meeting:

https://uaudio.zoom.us/j/91685441148
